    "<p>Kandinsky scholar; Professor of art history at the State University of New York in Binghamton.&nbsp; Lindsay was born to Kenneth C. Lindsay, a businessman, and Karen Eriksen (Lindsay).&nbsp; The younger Lindsay grew up in a staunch Republican family in Milwaukee, Wisconsin.": [
